#### Please describe the feature you would like to request.

I would like to be able to provide translation for the paginator labels.
Currently I'm using ngx-translate that provides a `.instant` method to load translations.  The problem with it is that it can't reload translations on reload. It only works if one navigates to the translated page from another page.

I'm assuming that there are something asynchronous happening with the instant method.

example (not working consistently): 

```ts
export function getTranslatePaginatorIntl(translate: TranslateService) {
  const paginatorIntl = new MatPaginatorIntl();

  paginatorIntl.itemsPerPageLabel = translate.instant(
    'paginator.itemsPerPageLabel'
  );
  paginatorIntl.firstPageLabel = translate.instant('paginator.firstPageLabel');
  paginatorIntl.previousPageLabel = translate.instant(
    'paginator.previousPageLabel'
  );
  paginatorIntl.nextPageLabel = translate.instant('paginator.nextPageLabel');
  paginatorIntl.lastPageLabel = translate.instant('paginator.lastPageLabel');

  return paginatorIntl;
}
```
